column11: Generic fly ash material.  Chemical composition and phase distribution based on that reported in X. Feng, E.J. Garboczi, D.P. Bentz, P.E. Stutzman, T.O. Mason, "Estimation of the degree of hydration of blended cement pastes by a scanning electron microscope point-counting procedure," Cem. Concr. Res. 34 [10] (2004) 1787-1793.
